76561198009939794,Recommended,312510,11783718,"Posted: 19 August, 2014",all,Rauke,"Charge, hoard and destroy!This polished 2D-Action-Platformer is ruthlessly easy to understand and frantic to play - especially with local friends.Imagine the action-laden gameplay of your typical Mario-Game, spiced up by being able to charge in four directions. Now imagine being almost invulnerable while charging, as well as being able to destroy blocks. By now you should feel very mobile and with new exciting combat-options to explore.This fun can be combined with up to three friends in four different, yet equally entertaining modes of competitive multiplayer.While this game isn't heavy on content and extras by any means, it really struck me and my friends by its quality: the gameplay feels fresh, well balanced and highly dynamic, the presentation feels coherent and quite stylish, the menus are very easy and effective to navigate.If you like your games to to be fun, direct, unique and with a little challenge, you should get this game."
